rComments: Absolutely loved this class. He's incredibly nice and understanding. And he tries to make this class as easy as possible. Definitely recommend it. You'll learn a lot of useful information and it's an easy A.

Awesome teacher, there is no book. Quizzes every week and a half to two weeks when homework is turned in. No tests throughout semester just a final exam. All quizzes and tests are multiple choice. Definitely recommended for crop sci students over organic chemistry. Much easier
